tee: @jeffstaple
recipe by cozycakes cottage<3

ingredients
for cake:
2 and ¼ cups flour (I use all-purpose flour. King Arthur brand is my favorite)
2 tsp. baking powder
1 tsp. baking soda
2 tsp. cinnamon
1 tsp. ground allspice
¾ tsp. nutmeg
½ tsp. ground ginger
¼ tsp. ground cloves
½ tsp. salt
1 and ⅓ cups canned pumpkin
¾ cup buttermilk
1 tsp. vanilla
1 cup unsalted butter, room temperature
1 cup granulated sugar
¼ cup brown sugar
3 eggs (I use extra-large)

for frosting:
¾ cup unsalted butter, room temperature
8 oz. cream cheese, room temperature
¾ tsp. vanilla
½ tsp. cinnamon
3 cups powdered sugar
1 Tbsp. milk

node.text:
JUGGERNAUT !!!

never get tired of dancing in the la heat. i’m so proud to create in a city that truly allows people to fully express themselves and feel limitless. always inspired by the energy in sunny los angeles. 🌞

@nikelosangeles #teamnike #ad

music: #juggernaut @feliciathegoat @liluzivert @pharrell 
videography: @vibrvncy @jyshih21 @hellojohnkim 
📍 @nikelosangeles

node.text:
saturday morning outdoor workout in my @nike gear 🌾

working out & breathing fresh air always keeps me motivated and centered. i’m always trying new things to keep my body moving! how do you stay active? @nikelosangeles #teamnike #ad
